---
title: Sweet & Spicy Hoisin Beef Tostadas with Tangy Slaw & Sriracha Mayo
description: Crispy tortillas make a perfect base for saucy ground pork and zesty coleslaw in this irresistible mash-up. Brown the pork with hoisin and chili sauces, load it onto those tostadas, then sprinkle on sesame seeds, pile on fresh slaw, and bring on the finale: a dollop of Sriracha mayo and squeeze of fresh lime juice to bring everything together.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/665def62bb68d6ba93ee197f-1e6d0df4.jpeg
